x4freetext: No explanation of relative units is given
The Li-7 target was prepared by evaporating metallic
lithium on to a pre-mounted carbon backing film.
However, a determination of the target mass cannot
readily be obtained either by direct weighing or by a
second exposure to measure the elastic scattering since
both procedures involve exposing the target to air.
Measurements of the absolute cross-sections are
therefore not possible.
